f6
{ We immediately challenge the bishop. Here we don't go for our ...Ne7-Ng6-Nxe5 plan.  5...Nge7  would also be possible. What I don't like is that after that, we are pinned and can't go ...Ng6 yet. The e5-pawn restricts the natural development of the knight to f6. We happily trade pawns to avoid that restriction. }
