{ White has difficulties developing the light-squared bishop. The two most popular moves at the 1600-level are both big mistakes. After  7.e3  we strike with  7...Bb4+  and after  8.Nbd2  h6  we force White to trade the bishop and break the pin on the knight. Study these variations here. }
