14. Qxg2 Nxg2
{ White played everything perfectly, and still, White has only one move in this position to maintain the advantage. }
15. d4
{ From move 5, White needs to find all these only moves to keep an advantage! These are ten only moves. Nobody at the 1600-level ever managed to reach this position. }
15... f6
{ Countering in the center and preventing the attack with Bg5. We have a lovely plan to play ...Nh4 followed by a deadly check with ...Nf3+. }
