7... Qg5 { Attacking and pinning the knight and also attacking the g2-pawn. }
8. Nxc6 { Discovered attacks are dangerous. } 8... Qxb5
{ Discovered attacks are dangerous, so we need to take measures. Black has a winning position. After  9.Nd4  we again attack the g2-pawn with  9...Qg5  . }
