{ The most popular move at 1600-level, whereas on top level  6.d4  is the most popular. }
6... Nc5
{ We will manage to trade White's strong light-squared bishop once again. } 7.
Nxe5
{ White is threatening a dangerous discovered attack, so we have to trade the knights. }
7... Nxe5 8. Rxe5+ Be7
{ A very comfortable position for Black that is easy to play. We will trade our knight for White's light-squared bishop, castle kingside, and play ...d6, attacking the rook and opening the diagonal for our light-squared bishop. }
