14. Nd4 Nxe5
{ We win the e5-pawn, and our knight is ready to jump with ...Nd3 or ...Nc4. Black has a winning position. After  15.Nxe6  forking the bishop and rook we strike with  15...Bxf2+  Black wins after  16.Kh1  e3!  . }
