[White "2b) Ruy Lopez Tactics and Model games "]
[Black "Exercise 6: Ruy Lopez"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "r1bqk2r/2p1bppp/p1np1n2/1p2p3/4P3/1BNP1N2/PPP2PPP/R1BQ1RK1 b kq - 0 8"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ What typical strategic idea do we have in this position? } 8... Na5
{ We manage to trade White's strong light-squared bishop for the knight and have a strategical advantage. We plan to castle and develop the light-squared bishop. }
