6. c3 Nge7
{ Developing the knight and preparing to castle. Also, we prepare to strike in the center with ...d5. }
7. Bb5 a6
{ Like in the Ruy Lopez, we force the bishop to move again. We would be happy to trade the light-squared bishop for our knight. }
