{ The most-played move for White at the 1600-level and a big mistake.  9.Rb1  doesn't work either since after  9...Bxb2  10.Rxb2  Qxc3+  forks the king and the rook. }
9... Qxc3
{ White cannot capture our queen since we are pinning the b2-pawn. After  10.bxa3  Qxa3+  Black has a devastating attack and a winning position. }
