{ How can we reach a significant advantage here? } 7... exf2+
{ A powerful intermediate check! White cannot recapture since this would lose the queen. }
8. Ke2 { The White king needs to keep touching his majesty. } 8... Qxd1+
{ We trade the queens before we recapture the bishop. } 9. Kxd1 Nxb4
{ Black has a significant advantage and easy development. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
