{ In this line, we prevent Qc2 before playing ...Qb6. Compared to the mainline,  5...Qb6  is less attractive, since after  6.Qb3  c4  7.Qc2  Bf5  8.Qxf5  Qxb2  , the rook isn't trapped. }
